reviewText:
I thought unauthorized meant not by the author, like an official autobiography.
I now know it it means "I didn't give this DvD authorization to be published.."
for official Taylor Swift merchandise please Visit the official Taylor Swift.com home page.

"Teardrops" low def video quality is poor, but the information was good.  It does have information not found in the other DVD's like this. I bought the "Fearless" DVD at the same time; which is more entertaining and memorable, so we enjoyed it a little more.
